    <div class="container-fluid">
        <div class="row jumbotron">
            <div class="col-xs-12 col-sm-12 col-md-9 col-lg-9 col-xl-10">
                <h1><b>Music portal</b> Web Application!</h1>
                <p class="lead">
                    The <b>"Music Portal"</b> Web site, where users can post and download songs.<br />
                    Songs on the site vary by genre and can only be added by registered users. 
                    New users can leave applications for registration, and are activated by the portal administrator.
                    The portal administrator can add, modify and delete users, genres of songs and songs.
                    All registered users can only add new songs to the genres created by the administrator and download music.
                    Users do not have access to delete or change.
                </p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
